high_descs: walk forwards a bit, then take a right and walk to the right side of the sink
grab the towel off of the towel holder
turn around and walk forwards a bit, then take a right and walk over to the right side of the toilet
place the towel on top of the toilet
turn around and face the sink directly behind you
grab the towel off of the towel holder to the left of the left sink
turn around and face the toilet again
place the towel on top of the toilet next to the other one
anns.task_desc: place two towels on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn right, head towards the grey bin, look up to find the hand towel on the silver towel ring holder.
Take the towel from the holder.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, turn left and face the toilet.
Hang the towel on the hanger above the toilet basin.
Turn around and face the sink.
Take the towel on the silver ring holder to your left.
Turn around and face the toilet.
Hang the towel on the hanger above the toilet basin.
anns.task_desc: Hang the two towels on the hanger above the toilet basin.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the towel holder on the wall.
Take the towel out of the holder.
Turn around and veer right to the toilet.
Put the towel on top of the toilet tank.
Turn around and look at the mirror.
Take the towel off the towel holder to your left.
Turn around and face the toilet again.
Place the towel on the toilet tank behind the first towel.
anns.task_desc: Put two towels on the toilet tank.
